{"tid":1059979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估刺身）刺身藏多條活寄生蟲 體長可達 40 厘米","createTime":"2019-03-13T12:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T15:24:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4931351635bba503673e88dd6c34f9d993bdf956","tid":1059979,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2290000/2292295/99C97D3A5C4819A029_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2290000%2F2292295%2F99C97D3A5C4819A029_1024.jpg&h=05598180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少人或許都有一個觀念，就是認定深海魚就沒有寄生蟲。其實這只風險比淡水魚低，但並非必然安全。早前在網絡上便流傳了一條影片，內容是在油甘魚內找出多條約長 10cm 的寄生蟲，部份更長達 30cm。<br />\n<br />\n【生活情報】女子愛吃三文魚刺身 肚藏 7 米長寄生蟲<br />\n<br />\n除了吞拿魚、三文魚外，油甘魚也是一種頗受食客歡迎的刺身。不過早前一條影片顯示，從油甘魚身上有時可以多個小孔，這些其實都是有寄生蟲鑽入而留下的徵狀。片中把油甘魚切開後，抽出多條紅色活的寄生蟲，由於色澤跟油甘魚相近，如果做成刺身，食客又沒小心看清，其實很易吃進肚子。<br />\n<br />\n據悉該條油甘魚的寄生蟲為「擬嗜子宮線蟲」（Philometroides seriolae），可生長至 40cm長。一條 30 厘米長的紅綫蟲可產出 600 至 800 萬條幼蟲，當中大部份會被浮游生物吃掉，其他油甘魚吃下浮游生物後再感染寄生蟲形成循環。人類如不慎吃了，寄生蟲及其分泌及排泄物可引致肚痛腹瀉及食物中毒。一般來說，油甘魚在春天會較易有這種寄生蟲，但至冬天則較少，所以影片指春夏不是吃油甘魚的好時候。<br />\n<br />\n除了這種寄生蟲外，港人常吃的三文魚、吞拿魚等海魚，都有可能有「海獸胃線蟲」，可令人腹瀉劇痛、嘔吐及急性腸胃炎。據政府食物安全中心建議，可透過冷凍方式處理；把供生吃的魚類在 -20&deg; C或以下冷凍 7 天；或在 -35&deg;C 冷凍約 20 小時，將魚體內的寄生蟲殺死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1fVJrrDs46I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1fVJrrDs46I&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=64de6c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1fVJrrDs46I</a>"},{"pid":"ae87b6c6e00e0b142a82c585cf813b91c63c72a7","tid":1059979,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2292295\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2292295&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BSSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=54be01d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2292295</a>"},{"pid":"d4e9b90789fb21f58f7d3c2fe9b73a5bb4b91654","tid":1059979,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f24cd7d65b39621e50eb1146291ba49d102210","tid":1059979,"uid":196964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"好想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e575b6a7753759dd8b122c1a59e5ea4b773f0ba","tid":1059979,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da56faf6ba5cb599e7d811de7bdbb1f4fc368410","tid":1059979,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"傻仔先食壽司同刺身"},{"pid":"5c315a79d0eddaace5f28a5248a56d7ace0bb3e7","tid":1059979,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"薄切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f50024f7e2084a2783338010bc3deabeec051d","tid":1059979,"uid":179364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:33:26.000Z","msg":"台灣？"},{"pid":"d5b084e0e91864c3619239db66c1a36e394759c5","tid":1059979,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"da56faf6ba5cb599e7d811de7bdbb1f4fc368410","tid":1059979,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"傻仔先食壽司同刺身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:07:48.000Z","msg":"話唔食刺身嗰啲人正白痴，依家低温殺蟲處理已經足以殺死所有寄生蟲，根本唔會有問題，如果真係有問題一早日日有寄生蟲新聞啦"},{"pid":"e1cbccddb874e59ad5302c2d0a12db94306ce028","tid":1059979,"ui